  "description": "It never sleeps. It has to keep moving because if it stopped, its magma body would cool and harden.",
  "flavorTexts": [
    {
      "text": "It never sleeps. It has to keep moving because if it stopped, its magma body would cool and harden.",
      "version": "gold"
    },
    {
      "text": "A common sight in volcanic areas, it slowly slithers around in a con­ stant search for warm places.",
      "version": "silver"
    },
    {
      "text": "These group to­ gether in areas that are hotter than normal. If it cools off, its skin hardens.",
      "version": "crystal"
    },
    {
      "text": "Molten magma courses throughout SLUGMA’s circulatory system. If this POKéMON is chilled, the magma cools and hardens. Its body turns brittle and chunks fall off, reducing its size.",
      "version": "ruby"
    },
    {
      "text": "SLUGMA does not have any blood in its body. Instead, intensely hot magma circulates throughout this POKéMON’s body, carrying essential nutrients and oxygen to its organs.",
      "version": "sapphire"
    }
  ],
